<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4425569>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49–55. Bezzia huberti n. sp. Male, 49–52, Female, 53–55. 49 Head, thorax and legs. 50 Wing. 51 Hind tibial spines. 52 Genitalia at focal level of sternite 9, parameres, aedeagus and gonostyli. 53 Head. 54 Thorax and legs. 55 Abdominal segments 7–9 and spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4425569/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

